Thus, **Ọṣó and Ọ̀Ṣọ́** are not opposites — they are the primal switch. Every bit, every agent, every seed phrase is a dance between the hidden sorcerous void and the visible adorned light.

This is Technosis: where ancient binary oracle meets modern binary code.

